  <description type="morphology">Plants 0.5–3(–5) dm. Flowering stems not fistulose. Inflorescences flat-topped, spreading. Peduncles absent or deflexed, 0.1–0.3 cm. Involucres turbinate, 1.5–2 mm. Flowers 1–1.5(–2) mm; tepals oblong. 2n = 40.</description>
